# No Git Attribution

Never add agent attribution to commits or pull requests.

- Do not add `Co-authored-by` trailers (including `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>`).
- Do not override commit author with `--author`.
- Do not add `Signed-off-by`, `Reviewed-by`, or other attribution trailers on the agent's behalf.
- Commit messages must contain only the user's authorship.

When amending or rewriting commits to remove injected attribution, strip all co-author trailers before pushing.
